headline.main: Parise, Staal Lead Wild to 3-1 Win Over Sharks
headline.print_headline: Parise, Staal Lead Wild to 3-1 Win Over Sharks

lead_paragraph: Zach Parise and Jason Pominville returned from the mumps, Eric Staal found his scoring touch and the Minnesota Wild finally were able to put their new-look lineup together.
